- Package.sh => argument versionType => type de version X.Y.Z (# X => major # Y => minor # Z => patch). Récupère la valeur dans package.json et incrémente le bon numéro


- Create new local git repo for api https://stackoverflow.com/questions/29994088/composer-require-local-package
cd ~/src/Foo && git init && echo -e "vendor\ncomposer.lock" > .gitignore && git add ./ && git commit -m "Initial Commit"
- Add this local repo into composer file
"require": {
    "sammitch/foo": "dev-master"
},
"repositories": [{
    "type": "vcs",
    "url": "/home/sammitch/src/Foo"
}],